# Local Saleor → Neon Postgres + Upstash Redis (no Docker db/cache).
# Copy to backend.env.neon-upstash and fill secrets (that file is gitignored).
#
# Prefer this path for BOTO (make up-neon). Shared-VM tunnel is legacy / Feed Me only.
#
# Neon project: polished-night-99206423 (BOTO) — pooled connection + sslmode=require.
# For flaky DDL during migrate, temporarily use the non-pooler host (drop "-pooler"
# from the hostname), then switch back to pooled for api/worker.
# Upstash Redis: 61f34aff-f963-4de0-ae1d-2c28b38cb235 (Boto) — read-write rediss:// URL.
# Do NOT use the default_ro / read-only Redis URL for CACHE_URL or CELERY_BROKER_URL.
#
# Upstash serverless Redis only supports DB index 0 (no SELECT /1,/2).
# Use the same Redis URL for CACHE_URL and CELERY_BROKER_URL; Celery and
# django-cache use different key namespaces.

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://neondb_owner:PASSWORD@ep-XXXX-pooler.REGION.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require
CACHE_URL=rediss://default:PASSWORD@YOUR-ENDPOINT.upstash.io:6379/0
CELERY_BROKER_URL=rediss://default:PASSWORD@YOUR-ENDPOINT.upstash.io:6379/0

SECRET_KEY=changeme
DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@example.com
EMAIL_URL=smtp://mailpit:1025
OTEL_SERVICE_NAME=saleor
OTEL_TRACES_EXPORTER=otlp
OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://jaeger:4317
